{"id":150,"ayahs":[{"number":158,"arabic":"هَلْ يَنظُرُونَ إِلَّآ أَن تَأْتِيَهُمُ ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ أَوْ يَأْتِىَ رَبُّكَ أَوْ يَأْتِىَ بَعْضُ ءَايَٰتِ رَبِّكَ ۗ يَوْمَ يَأْتِى بَعْضُ ءَايَٰتِ رَبِّكَ لَا يَنفَعُ نَفْسًا إِيمَٰنُهَا لَمْ تَكُنْ ءَامَنَتْ مِن قَبْلُ أَوْ كَسَبَتْ فِىٓ إِيمَٰنِهَا خَيْرًۭا ۗ قُلِ ٱنتَظِرُوٓا۟ إِنَّا مُنتَظِرُونَ","translation":"Do they, perchance, wait for the angels to appear unto them, or for thy Sustainer [Himself] to appear, or for some of thy Sustainer's [final] portents to appear? [But] on the Day when thy Sustainer's [final] portents do appear, believing will be of no avail to any human being who did not believe before, or who, while believing, did no good works. Say: \"Wait, [then, for the Last Day, O unbelievers:] behold, we [believers] are waiting, too!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/947.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":81567,"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81568,"position":2,"arabic":"يَنظُرُونَ","translation":"তারা অপেক্ষা করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81569,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81570,"position":4,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81571,"position":5,"arabic":"تَأْتِيَهُمُ","translation":"কাছে আসবে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81572,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","translation":"ফেরেশতারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81573,"position":7,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81574,"position":8,"arabic":"يَأْتِىَ","translation":"আসবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":81575,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_158